{"tid":21680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"📰德醫科女學生遭姦殺 17歲阿富汗難民被捕","createTime":"2016-12-04T04:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T09:01:38.000Z","uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8009dccf0d7edc33e7d0fe9d967a835276c92a95","tid":21680,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:16:45.000Z","msg":"一名阿富汗青年難民，涉嫌在德國姦殺一名19歲女學生，被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n案發在德國西南城市弗賴堡(Freiburg)，警方在兇案現場發現17歲疑犯的DNA，並透過現場的閉路電視片段，把疑兇拘捕。<br />\n疑兇去年隻身抵達德國，被安置在寄養家庭。而案中死者是一名醫科學生，今年10月中一個晚上，她與同學外出聚會，之後騎單車回家，但數小時後，有人發現她倒斃一條河邊，驗屍證實她是溺斃。調查暫未發現死者與疑兇有任何連繫。<br />\n此案發生後不足一個月，一名27歲女子外出緩跑時遭姦殺，案件仍未偵破，不過警方表示未發現兩宗案件有關連。<br />\n阿富汗青年疑犯落網的消息引起網民激烈反應，不少人在社交網站向總理默克爾反諷地說「多謝你！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161204/56001836\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161204%2F56001836&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=d498283f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161204%2F56001836&h=4e5f1aad\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161204/56001836</a>"},{"pid":"1a1a1c060865e45b53796d1c0c424376b953ae83","tid":21680,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:17:52.000Z","msg":"點解唔包容？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n難民都有性需要"},{"pid":"da69b8b00417d6e132139e3e3213949d115f7ca4","tid":21680,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"包容"},{"pid":"517f2181dd7548aa0f31c5a77287544e29f8dc05","tid":21680,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:21:48.000Z","msg":"多謝蕭山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea7effcb33f1b70e0a6218b877e1a056fc6b424","tid":21680,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc